7. Unit tests — `packages/exploration_agent/test/loop_driver/default_loop_host_test.dart`

   Use `ExplorationSession.forTest(VmServiceClient.forTest(fakeVm, 'iso'))`
   with a `_FakeVmService` subclassing `VmService` and overriding
