Commit: `refactor(exploration_flutter): extract _wirePlugins shared install path`

### 3. Implement `ExplorationBinding.run` — same file

Add `import 'exploration_app.dart';` at top. Add static method after `ensureInitialized`:

```dart
static void run(ExplorationApp app) {
  if (kReleaseMode) {
    final cfg = app.build(_ReleaseContext());
    runApp(cfg.app);
    return;
  }
  if (_instance == null) {
    final existing = BindingBase.debugBindingType();
    if (existing != null && existing != ExplorationBinding) {
      throw StateError(
        'ExplorationBinding.run cannot install: another WidgetsBinding '
        '($existing) is already active. Make ExplorationBinding.run(...) '
        'the first Flutter-touching line of main() — construct shared '
        'instances (Router, Dio, ProviderContainer) inside '
        'ExplorationApp.build, not before.');
    }
    final binding = ExplorationBinding._(
      <ExplorationPlugin>[], const <String>[], kDefaultErrorBufferCapacity);
    _instance = binding;
    final cfg = app.build(_DebugContext(binding));
    binding._wirePlugins(cfg.plugins);
    runZoned<void>(() => runApp(cfg.app),
        zoneSpecification: stabilityZoneSpec(binding));
  } else {
    // Idempotent: prior run/ensureInitialized already installed.
    final cfg = app.build(_DebugContext(_instance!));
    runZoned<void>(() => runApp(cfg.app),
        zoneSpecification: stabilityZoneSpec(_instance!));
  }
}
```

File-private context impls at end of file:

```dart
class _DebugContext implements ExplorationAppContext {
  _DebugContext(this._b);
  final ExplorationBinding _b;
  @override ExplorationBinding? get binding => _b;
  @override bool get isProductionMode => false;
  @override void onTeardown(Future<void> Function() cb) => _b._teardowns.add(cb);
}
class _ReleaseContext implements ExplorationAppContext {
  @override ExplorationBinding? get binding => null;
  @override bool get isProductionMode => true;
  @override void onTeardown(Future<void> Function() cb) {}
}
```

Update `debugReset` to drain teardowns LIFO and become async; `resetForTesting` becomes `static Future<void> resetForTesting() => debugReset();`:

```dart
static Future<void> debugReset() async {
  final b = _instance;
  if (b != null) {
    while (b._teardowns.isNotEmpty) { await b._teardowns.removeLast()(); }
    b._uninstallErrorHooks();
  }
  _instance = null;
}
```

Add two `@visibleForTesting` helpers in the binding class:

```dart
@visibleForTesting
void debugSetTeardownsForTesting(List<Future<void> Function()> v) {
  _teardowns..clear()..addAll(v);
}
@visibleForTesting
Future<void> debugDrainTeardownsForTesting() async {
  while (_teardowns.isNotEmpty) { await _teardowns.removeLast()(); }
}
```

