4. **`PromptAssembler.assemble`** — `packages/exploration_agent/lib/src/prompt/prompt_assembler.dart` (new file)

   Returns the existing `PromptPayload` (cx6.14). System message concatenates AGENTS.md + goal + summary + recent actions; user messages carry serialized observation + diff; tools list passes through unchanged.

   ```dart
   class PromptAssembler {
     const PromptAssembler();

     PromptPayload assemble({
       required String agentsMd,
       required String goal,
       required RunningSummary summary,
       required ActionRing actionRing,
       required Observation observation,
       required ObservationDiff diff,
       required List<ToolDescriptor> mergedTools,
     }) {
       final actionLines = actionRing.entries.join('\n');
       final systemMessage = StringBuffer()
         ..writeln(agentsMd)
         ..writeln()
         ..writeln('## Goal')
         ..writeln(goal)
         ..writeln()
         ..writeln('## Running summary')
         ..writeln(summary.text)
         ..writeln()
         ..writeln('## Recent actions')
         ..writeln(actionLines.isEmpty ? '(none yet)' : actionLines);

       return PromptPayload(
         systemMessage: systemMessage.toString().trimRight(),
         userMessages: <Map<String, dynamic>>[
           <String, dynamic>{
             'type': 'text',
             'text': 'Observation:\n${jsonEncode(observation.toJson())}',
           },
           <String, dynamic>{
             'type': 'text',
             'text': 'Diff since last turn:\n${jsonEncode(diff.toJson())}',
           },
         ],
         tools: List<ToolDescriptor>.unmodifiable(mergedTools),
       );
     }
   }
   ```

